    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six power plant paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The high-revving naturally aspirated engine remains exceptionally responsive across the power band, benefitting from a recently overhauled VANOS system and verified rod bearing clearances. To ensure chassis integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with plates\u2014a critical preventive measure for this platform. The drivetrain is anchored by a functional variable M differential lock, providing excellent mechanical grip and predictable torque distribution. It features a refreshed suspension setup with polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the precise turn-in and tactile feedback synonymous with the E46 chassis. While showing honest signs of spirited use, the mechanical vitals are robust and the compression across all six cylinders remains within factory spec.",
